        SAGE_WALAHRA_WAS_THE_FOUNDER_OF_THE_PHILOSOPHY                                              = 10626,  -- Sage Walahra was the founder of the philosophy From the void all things are born. To the void all things return. Without a full understanding of those words, one shall never approach the fundamental truth of existence.
