        QUITE_SOME_TIME_AGO_THERE_WAS_AN_ABSOLUTELY                                                 = 10631,  -- Quite some time ago, there was an absolutely horrifying epidemic in Bastok, one of the nations of the Middle Lands. It was referred to as the Bastokan Blight.
