        THOSE_WHO_HAVE_BEEN_STRIPPED_DIPPED_OF_THEIR                                                = 10664,  -- Those who have been stripped-dipped of their citizenship and those who never had it in the first place live in the Commoners' Ward. It's a relatively new area.
        PEOPLE_WHO_HAVE_COME_FROM_OTHER_NATIONS_AND                                                 = 10665,  -- People who have come from other nations and the merchants who sell to them live in the Merchants' Ward. It's a smorgasbord of sights and smells. There are also two ports that allow Aht Urhgan Whitegate to serve as the main gate to West Aht Urhgan.
        THE_IMPERIAL_WARD_LIES_BEYOND_THOSE_TOWERING_IVORY                                          = 10666,  -- The Imperial Ward lies beyond those towering ivory walls. It houses the Imperial palace, facilities for the Imperial Army, and the residences of the Imperial family. People like us aren't even allowed to enter.
        IN_ANCIENT_TIMES_THERE_EXISTED_AN_ADVANCED_CIVILIZATION                                     = 10667,  -- In ancient times, there existed an advanced civilization called the Empire of Alzadaal.
        EMPEROR_ALZADAAL_HAD_THE_POWER_TO_CONTROL_AN                                                = 10668,  -- Emperor Alzadaal had the power to control an enormous humanoid that he used to conquer the surrounding nations. Utilizing this mysterious power, he built the foundation of an enormous empire.
        EVERY_CHILD_IN_AHT_URHGAN_KNOWS_THAT_FAIRY                                                  = 10669,  -- Every child in Aht Urhgan knows that fairy tale. Did you?
        HEY_LISTEN_UP_I_SAW_SOMETHING_ABSOLUTELY_UNBERRY                                            = 10670,  -- Hey, listen up! I saw something absolutely unberry-lievable! It was a Yagudo. Yes, a Yagudo! Do you know what I'm talking about? A Yagudo in town, of all places!
        NOT_ONLY_THAT_BUT_HE_WAS_SIPPER_SIPPING                                                     = 10671,  -- Not only that, but he was sipper-sipping a cup of chai at the teahouse! Can you believe that? That kind of thing would never, ever happen in Windurst!
        I_MEAN_THAT_S_LIKE_TALKY_WALKING_INTO                                                       = 10672,  -- I mean, that's like talky-walking into the Rarab Tail Hostelry one day and...boom! There's a Yagudo sitting in the corner eating his lunch with a little napkin on his lap! I mean, this is a Yagudo we're talking about here!
        MY_FRIENDS_IN_WINDURST_ARE_NEVER_GONNA_BELIEVE                                              = 10673,  -- My friends in Windurst are never gonna believe me when I tell them...
        IF_YOU_STICK_AROUND_IN_THIS_TOWN_LONG                                                       = 10674,  -- If you stick around in this town long enough, I'm sure you'll see him yourself...a Yagudo tea aficionado! Now I've seen everything!
        YOU_WILL_NEVER_GUESS_WHAT_I_SAW_HE                                                          = 10675,  -- You will never guess what I saw! He was right in front of me...the dreamiest man I had ever laid eyes on!
        CAN_YOU_IMAGINE_MY_SURPRISE_HE_WAS_COVERED                                                  = 10676,  -- Can you imagine my surprise? He was covered from head to toe in golden armor. He was so stunning I was forced to shade my eyes!
        NOT_ONLY_THAT_BUT_HE_WAS_SO_GENEROUS                                                        = 10677,  -- Not only that, but he was so generous! He treated everyone in the teahouse to all the chai and coffee we could drink! Have you ever heard anything like it? <Sigh>...
        TETEROON_AT_YOOOR_SERVICE_TETEROON_IS_MEEERCENARY                                           = 10678,  -- Teteroon at yooor service! Teteroon is meeercenary.
        THREE_CHEERS_FOOOR_THE_EMPREEESS_JUST_LITTLE_JOOOKE                                         = 10679,  -- Three cheers fooor the Empreeess! ...Just little joooke. Ha ha!
        YOU_APPEAR_TO_BE_AN_ADVENTURER_ARE_YOU                                                      = 10680,  -- You appear to be an adventurer. Are you aware that there is a place called the Chamber of Passage in this town?
        APPARENTLY_IT_ALLOWS_YOU_TO_BE_INSTANTLY_TRANSPORTED                                        = 10681,  -- Apparently, it allows you to be instantly transported to an area that you have previously visited...of all things!
        THEN_AGAIN_I_WONDER_HOW_MUCH_TRUTH_THERE                                                    = 10682,  -- Then again, I wonder how much truth there is in such tales. After all, people also insist that there are ships that can fly in the sky!
        THEY_SAY_THIS_AUCTION_HOUSE_IS_CONNECTED_WITH                                               = 10683,  -- They say this auction house is connected with another auction house located in the Grand Duchy of Jeuno.
        THERE_ARE_RUMORS_THAT_SOME_DUBIOUS_FOLK_CALLED                                              = 10684,  -- There are rumors that some dubious folk called the Tenshodo are somehow behind it all.
        AN_AMAZING_VARIETY_OF_WARES_ARE_SOLD_DAILY                                                  = 10685,  -- An amazing variety of wares are sold daily in Jeuno's auction house. It's huge business!
        THANKS_TO_THE_TENSHODO_MY_GOODS_ARE_SELLING                                                 = 10686,  -- Thanks to the Tenshodo, my goods are selling faster than ever before!
        THERE_ARE_TWO_TYPES_OF_DRINKS_HERE_AT                                                       = 10687,  -- There are two types of drinks here at the Shararat Teahouse--coffee and chai. The coffee appeals to the traditionalists and allows the shop to retain its atmosphere...
        BUT_THEY_MADE_A_WISE_DECISION_BY_ALSO                                                       = 10688,  -- But they made a wise decision by also introducing chai, which is newer and cheaper than coffee. Now, this teahouse is extremely popular with young people, and is always bustling with activity. A brilliant business move, don't you think?
        I_JUST_CAN_T_DECIDE_WHETHER_I_IDENTIFY                                                      = 10689,  -- I just can't decide whether I identify more with the coffee crowd or the chai crowd!
        MY_MOM_TOLD_ME_THAT_RICH_PEOPLE_LIVE                                                        = 10690,  -- My mom told me that rich people live on the other side of that wall...
        SHE_SAID_WE_CAN_T_GO_OVER_THERE                                                             = 10691,  -- She said we can't go over there because we're poor. Why can't we be rich, too?
        DID_YOU_KNOW_THAT_COFFEE_WILL_MAKE_YOU                                                      = 10692,  -- Did you know that coffee will make you feel really nice if you just pour a bag of maple sugar into it? Even I can drink it, then!
