        HMMM_MIGHT_IT_HAVE_BEEN_SOME_FAR_EASTERN                                                    = 12162,  -- Hmmm...might it have been some Far Eastern ninja spy? A Lamia hitwoman? This story reeks...of untapped potential!
        I_HAD_HOPED_AS_MUCH_AS_IT_HAPPENS                                                           = 12163,  -- I had hoped as much. As it happens, the detective originally assigned to the case by the Imperial Palace is one of my regulars. Shall I introduce you?
