        HOWEVER_MISSION_OBJECTIVES_WITHIN_THE_NYZUL_ISLE_REMNANTS                                   = 12893,  -- However, mission objectives within the Nyzul Isle remnants are handled with the utmost confidentiality. Your mission orders will all be received from the on-site Assault commander.
