        DEPOSITING_NYZUL_TOKENS_INTO_THEM_WILL_YIELD_ARTIFACTS                                      = 12905,  -- Depositing Nyzul tokens into them will yield artifacts usable only in the immediate environs. By what ancient technology or magic they operate, we do not know.
