        WELCOME_TO_THE_NYZUL_ISLE_FIELD_STATION_OF                                                  = 12913,  -- Welcome to the Nyzul Isle field station of the Aht Urhgan Archaeological Research Institute. It is here that we conduct our most pioneering research, undeterred by the threat of danger that lurks in every nook of these ruins.
