        THOUGH_THE_ASTRARIA_WE_HAVE_UNEARTHED_HAVE_BEEN                                             = 12925,  -- Though the astraria we have unearthed have been far too weathered and waterlogged to serve their original function, they have proven a veritable treasure trove of insight into the civilization that created them.
