        WELL_MET_I_M_A_MERRY_MAP_MARKER                                                             = 14340,  -- Well met! I'm a Merry Map Marker, and I'd love to make marks all over your merry %, but it appears you are missing the markable map I mention.
        GOOD_DAY_I_M_A_MERRY_MAP_MARKER                                                             = 14341,  -- Good day! I'm a Merry Map Marker, and I'd be emphatically ecstatic if you'd allow me to mark your magical map!
        A_MARKLESS_IS_LIKE_A_MOTHERLESS_MAIDEN_MEANDERING                                           = 14342,  -- A markless % is like a motherless maiden, meandering through a miasmatic mire of misery.
        EMBARK_ON_A_MAP_MARKING_MISSION_MARK_ME                                                     = 14343,  -- Embark on a map-marking mission? Mark me up! Keep your mitts off my map!
        MARVELOUS_NOW_ALLOW_ME_A_MINUTE_TO_MAKE                                                     = 14344,  -- Marvelous! Now allow me a minute to make all my marks.
        METHINKS_I_HAVE_MARKED_YOUR_MAP_WITH_AS                                                     = 14345,  -- Methinks I have marked your map with as many marks as I might manage.
        MONITORING_AND_MANAGING_YOUR_MARKS_IS_AS_SIMPLE                                             = 14346,  -- Monitoring and managing your marks is as simple as merely opening your map and selecting Markers from the main menu.
        IF_THE_MARKS_ON_YOUR_MAP_MIGHT_VANISH                                                       = 14347,  -- If the marks on your map might vanish, mope not like a melancholy milksop. Make another meeting with me and I shall make it my mission to mark the map once more.
        GOOD_DAY_MILORD_MILADY_MAY_YOUR_MARCHES_ACROSS                                              = 14348,  -- Good day, milord/milady]. May your marches across meadow and mountain be markedly memorable!
        HERE_IS_THE_AREA_S_HOME_POINT_ONCE                                                          = 14349,  -- Here is the area's home point. Once set, your muted remains will be moved here if you are ever...mortally mangled in the midst of a melee.
        HERE_YOU_WILL_FIND_THE_IMMIGRATION_MINISTERS_THEY                                           = 14350,  -- Here you will find the immigration ministers. They will help you if you may wish to immediately modify your nationality.
        AND_MAYHAP_YOU_ARE_IMMEASURABLY_MOTIVATED_TO_COMPETE                                        = 14351,  -- And mayhap you are immeasurably motivated to compete in the medieval mayhem of Conflict? Might I suggest you mingle with the modest Pursuivant located here?
        OUR_LOCAL_MINSTREL_OF_MELODIES_CAN_BE_FOUND                                                 = 14352,  -- Our local minstrel of melodies can be found here. His mirthful musicalities may help you recall misplaced memories.
        AH_AND_IN_THE_CASE_YOU_MIGHT_WISH                                                           = 14353,  -- Ah, and in the case you might wish to mask a meritorious moniker and replace it with one a mite more merited, a traveling bard strums upon his mellifluous harp here.
        HERE_YOU_MAY_MEET_WITH_A_MEMBER_OF                                                          = 14354,  -- Here, you may meet with a member of the Specialty Goods Trade Union. And, if you are a citizen of this mighty dominion, he'll teleport you all across Vana'diel (for a menial amount of monetary remuneration).
        NEED_TO_KNOW_THE_LOCAL_WEATHER_OUR_LOCAL                                                    = 14355,  -- Need to know the local weather? Our local meteorologist will be making his paramount presumptions here.
        IF_YOU_WISH_TO_SUMMON_A_MERCIFUL_MATE                                                       = 14356,  -- If you wish to summon a merciful mate to this mighty realm, here is where you will find a merry merchant marketing Gold World Passes.
        THOSE_MEN_AND_WOMEN_WONDERING_HOW_THEIR_DEEDS                                               = 14357,  -- Those men and women wondering how their deeds are mirrored in the minds of the locals should meander over to this gossip-meister to muster up important material on their respective reputations.
        THE_ARMOR_DEPOSITORY_LOCATED_HERE_WILL_HELP_YOU                                             = 14358,  -- The armor depository located here will help you maintain any old sets of equipment muddling up your immaculate Mog House.
        AND_HERE_IS_THE_ITEM_DEPOSITORY_WHERE_YOU                                                   = 14359,  -- And here is the item depository where you may store much of your festive furniture, etcetera until misplaced holiday merriment makes it way back into your miserly heart.
        LET_ME_BEGIN_WITH_SOUTHERN_SAN_D_ORIA                                                       = 14360,  -- Let me begin with Southern San d'Oria.
        NOW_I_SHALL_MOVE_TO_NORTHERN_SAN_D                                                          = 14361,  -- Now I shall move to Northern San d'Oria.
