        NEXT_LET_ME_MARK_YOUR_MAP_OF_UPPER                                                          = 14373,  -- Next, let me mark your map of Upper Jeuno. Did you know that I often frequent the Marble Bridge whenever I have a free moment? There's just something about the name of that model establishment...
