        HMPH_I_M_AFRAID_I_JUST_CAN_T                                                                = 14405,  -- Hmph. I'm afraid I just can't wrap my head around the potentially outlandish expenses that this undertaking would incur. Just think of the risks involved. And as anyone knows, no expense is sparrred when it comes to the safety of my mercenaries.
        ISN_T_THAT_RIGHT_CAPTAIN_WHAT_DO_YOU                                                        = 14406,  -- Isn't that right, Captain %? What do you think?
