        AS_MY_ATTENDANT_OF_COURSE                                                                   = 14441,  -- As my attendant, of course.
        OH_AND_I_LL_BE_HANGING_ONTO_THIS                                                            = 14442,  -- Oh, and I'll be hanging onto this weapon for now. For safekeeping. I hate to pull rrrank on you, but you were under orders when you happened to find it. And it is I who gives the orders around here, after all. So simple logic tells us who should keep it.
