        SIMPLY_AMAZING_YOU_VE_MANAGED_TO_RECOVER_YET                                                = 14458,  -- Simply amazing! You've managed to recover yet another weapon!?
        SURE_ENOUGH_THIS_ONE_IS_RRRESONATING_WITH_THE                                               = 14459,  -- Sure enough, this one is rrresonating with the quartz transmitter as well. Looks like we have another winner!
