        IT_SEEMS_MY_PROPOSALS_HAVEN_T_BEEN_FALLING                                                  = 14466,  -- It seems my proposals haven't been falling entirely on deaf ears after all. The Empress herself seems to have taken notice of the counsel I've been prrroviding.
        AS_YOU_MAY_OR_MAY_NOT_KNOW_THE                                                              = 14467,  -- As you may or may not know, the Empire is ceaselessly pursuing to advance relations with the beastmen via peaceful negotiations. But rrrecently, some chieftains have been hampering progress, and proving to be quite the thorns in the proverbial side.
        ONLY_AFTER_READING_THE_IMPERIAL_ORDERS_THEY_SEEM                                            = 14468,  -- Only... After reading the Imperial orders, they seem to be a bit... Well, lenient.
        SO_HERE_S_HOW_WE_RE_GOING_TO                                                                = 14469,  -- So, here's how we're going to do this. First rrrule of upper management, Captain %. Change what you don't like!
        I_WANT_YOU_TO_GO_AND_DROP_THESE                                                             = 14470,  -- I want you to go and drop these chieftains like a bad habit!
        THERE_ARE_THREE_SPECIFIC_TARGETS_WE_RE_AFTER                                                = 14471,  -- There are three specific targets we're after. You sure you got the sand for this one, Captain?
        FIRST_GURFURLUR_THE_MENACING_THE_CHIEFTAIN_WHO_HOLDS                                        = 14472,  -- First, Gurfurlur the Menacing, the chieftain who holds sway over Halvung and all the trrrolls that infest it.
        NEXT_THE_RUTHLESS_MAMOOL_JA_LEADER_GULOOL_JA                                                = 14473,  -- Next, the ruthless Mamool Ja leader, Gulool Ja Ja, tyrant of Mamook.
        AND_FINALLY_THE_FOUL_LAMIA_WITCH_MEDUSA_WHO                                                 = 14474,  -- And finally, the foul Lamia witch Medusa, who commands her Undead Swarm from the evil rrreaches of Arrapago Reef.
        THINK_YOU_CAN_REMEMBER_ALL_THAT_THIS_COULD                                                  = 14475,  -- Think you can remember all that? This could be the mission that breaks you, %. Think of it! The mercenary of humble beginnings who felled the thrrree beastkings. The stuff of legends, I tell ya.
        UNFORTUNATELY_THE_BEASTKINGS_BECOME_EVEN_STRONGER_AS_THE                                    = 14476,  -- Unfortunately, the beastkings become even stronger as the beastmen rrranks grow in number.
        WELL_I_M_SURE_YOU_LL_MANAGE_TO                                                              = 14477,  -- Well, I'm sure you'll manage to get the job done, Captain. However, if you encounter any prrroblems, there is one trick you can use...
        THE_BEASTKINGS_CAN_SOMETIMES_BE_FOUND_AWAY_FROM                                             = 14478,  -- The beastkings can sometimes be found away from their main base. Their defenses are usually thin, making it the perrrfect time to strike while their guard is down.
        GURFURLUR_HAS_BEEN_SPOTTED_IN_THE_NAVUKGO_EXECUTION                                         = 14479,  -- Gurfurlur has been spotted in the Navukgo Execution Chamber, while Gulool Ja Ja was seen in Jade Sepulcher, and you can find Medusa in Talacca Cove.
        SO_IF_YOU_RE_HEADED_THAT_WAY_MAKE                                                           = 14480,  -- So if you're headed that way, make sure you don't let them get the better of you!
