        AND_IN_CASE_YOU_DIDN_T_KNOW_THEY                                                            = 14491,  -- And in case you didn't know, they're capable of self-replication. At this rate, if they continue to escape from the ruins unchecked, their numbers will multiply to the extent that... Well, let's just say that the Empire wouldn't stand a chance and leave it at that.
        SO_WHAT_WE_VE_GOT_TO_DO_IS                                                                  = 14492,  -- So what we've got to do is somehow get to the units giving the orders, these command chariots, and bust them up rrreal good.
        FIRST_THERE_S_THE_BATTLECLAD_CHARIOT_THAT_RRRESIDES                                         = 14493,  -- First, there's the Battleclad Chariot that rrresides deep in the Zhayolm Remnants.
        THEN_THERE_S_THE_ARMORED_CHARIOT_THAT_LURKS                                                 = 14494,  -- Then there's the Armored Chariot that lurks somewhere in the Arrapago Remnants.
        ALSO_THE_LONG_BOWED_CHARIOT_YOU_LL_BE                                                       = 14495,  -- Also, the Long-Bowed Chariot. You'll be able to find that one in the Bhaflau Remnants.
        AND_LASTLY_THE_LONG_ARMED_CHARIOT_THAT_ONE                                                  = 14496,  -- And lastly, the Long-Armed Chariot. That one should be rrroaming around in the Silver Sea Remnants.
        THOSE_ARE_YOUR_FOUR_TARGETS                                                                 = 14497,  -- Those are your four targets.
        IT_S_NOT_OFTEN_I_GET_EMOTIONAL_BUT                                                          = 14498,  -- It's not often I get emotional, but the safety of the Empire, and dare I say the entire world, may be at stake here. So get to it, Captain!
