        YOUR_RENOWN_IS_CERTAINLY_NOT_UNDESERVED_I_MUST                                              = 14501,  -- Your renown is certainly not undeserved. I must admit, I am quite impressed.
        IT_S_LIKE_I_VE_ALWAYS_SAID_IF                                                               = 14502,  -- It's like I've always said. If the exemplary performances of our mercenaries prove anything, it is the worth and quality of the training rrregimen I personally devised. You keep doing good by me, Captain %, and you just might turn out all right.
        THAT_FOREBODING_VISAGE_KNOWN_AS_THE_DARK_RIDER                                              = 14503,  -- That foreboding visage known as the Dark Rider is now known to be none other than the nefarious god Odin himself. Reliable sources have confirmed rrrumors that he regularly haunts the Hazhalm Testing Grounds.
        AND_AS_YOU_MAY_HAVE_HEARD_THE_EMPRESS                                                       = 14504,  -- And as you may have heard, the Empress has been making great strides towards reconciliation with opposition forces through such acts as the establishment of the Seagull Phratrie.
        NOT_SURE_WHAT_TO_MAKE_OF_IT_ALL                                                             = 14505,  -- Not sure what to make of it all, to be honest. Seems like every auspicious omen we see is offset by an equally ominous one in turn. And all the while everyone is resting on their laurrrels! It's a complete deadlock and something must be done!
        YOU_GUESSED_IT_THAT_S_WHERE_YOU_COME                                                        = 14506,  -- You guessed it. That's where you come in!
