        THE_SINGULAR_AIM_OF_THIS_MISSION_IS_TO                                                      = 14509,  -- The singular aim of this mission is to banish Odin back to wherever it is that he may have been spewed forth from.
        I_WON_T_LIE_TO_YOU_CAPTAIN_THIS                                                             = 14510,  -- I won't lie to you, Captain. This will not be over quickly. You will not enjoy this. Your opponent may be a god, but he is not your god. Go send this foul deity back under his rock, before the situation becomes too dirrre!
        WHAT_I_CAN_T_BELIEVE_WHAT_I_M                                                               = 14511,  -- What!? I can't believe what I'm hearing! You're telling me you succeeded in banishing Odin back into darkness? Just like that?
        WE_ARE_TALKING_ABOUT_THE_SAME_ODIN_RIGHT                                                    = 14512,  -- We are talking about the same Odin, right? The Odin that not even the Immortals themselves could best? I don't know how you do it, %. And I'm not sure I want to...
        IT_NEVER_CEASES_TO_AMAZE_ME_THAT_MY                                                         = 14513,  -- It never ceases to amaze me that my humble institution here could instill such grrreatness into an otherwise mundane adventurer.
        THAT_S_MY_ALWAYS_TAKING_CARE_OF_BUSINESS                                                    = 14514,  -- That's my %! Always taking care of business. Though I can't deny that some of the credit is due in part to my behind-the-scenes guidance.
        WELL_THAT_S_ALL_YOU_RE_GONNA_GET                                                            = 14515,  -- Well, that's all you're gonna get by way of a debrrriefing. Might not be a lot, but I'm not entirely opposed to leaping before you look. There's something to be said for taking the initiative and surging forward. As long as there are results to show for it, mind you. Now get on it!
        WELL_WELL_WELL_IF_IT_ISN_T_THE                                                              = 14516,  -- Well, well, well. If it isn't the great Captain %. You honor us with your prrresence.
        IT_WOULD_SEEM_YOU_VE_GONE_AND_COMPLETED                                                     = 14517,  -- It would seem you've gone and completed all three of the Empress's objectives. Purged the beastkings, dismantled the chariots, and banished the mighty Odin. Quite the rrresume you're building.
        I_SUPPOSE_THE_EMPRESS_SHOULD_BE_GETTING_IN                                                  = 14518,  -- I suppose the Empress should be getting in touch with us any time n--
