        IN_ACCORDANCE_WITH_THE_WILL_OF_HER_HIGHNESS                                                 = 14555,  -- %. In accordance with the will of Her Highness, the Empire wishes to bestow upon you this gift in recognition of your services. You continue to honor us all with your allegiance.
