        RATHER_THAN_WASTING_AWAY_AS_AN_ARTIFACT_IN                                                  = 14617,  -- Rather than wasting away as an artifact in the treasury catacombs, no doubt this % would be put to better use in the hands of a true champion of the Empire. That was its original purpose, after all.
