        TO_THE_HONORABLE_WE_TRUST_THIS_MISSIVE_FINDS                                                = 14828,  -- To the Honorable %-- We trust this missive finds you well and continuing your extraordinary service to the Empire. We were particularly overjoyed to hear of your recent exploits, inasmuch as--
