        THANK_YOU_FOR_COMING_WE_APOLOGIZE_FOR_SUMMONING                                             = 14989,  -- Thank you for coming, %. We apologize for summoning you so abruptly.
        ALLOW_ME_TO_GET_STRAIGHT_TO_THE_POINT                                                       = 14990,  -- Allow me to get straight to the point. We have observed another set of disturbing readings coming from the distortion at Nyzul Isle. I fear that Alexander is once more on the verge of breaching through to our world.
