        THERE_S_NO_MISTAKING_THE_TWIN_EMBLEMS_OF                                                    = 15046,  -- There's no mistaking the twin emblems of the crowned dolphin and the Dark Rider.
        THANK_YOU_THERE_S_SOMEONE_WHO_WILL_BE                                                       = 15047,  -- Thank you, %. There's someone who will be very happy to see this. In fact, why don't you come along?
