        AH_PERHAPS_TO_THOSE_WHO_FASHIONED_IT_IT                                                     = 15078,  -- Ah, perhaps to those who fashioned it, it was merely that. A simple charm fashioned with a simple invocation, that Ephramadian soldiers might be blessed with divine grace in battle.
